dc_description_s: This data layer represents parcels for Rusk County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Rusk_Parcels_2016.gdb.[The published representation of real property areas, combined with assessing and tax information from CAMA and Tax systems, and organized for consumption in desktop and web applications. This feature class contains redundant geometry in cases where there are multiple condominium units on a given tax parcel]
